                "Upgrade vCenter to version 9.1 using VCF Operations through Fleet Management - All Guidance is provided in link (<a href='https://techdocs.broadcom.com/us/en/vmware-cis/vcf/vcf-9-0-and-later/9-1/deployment/upgrading-cloud-foundation/upgrade-the-management-domain-to-vmware-cloud-foundation-5-2/updating-vcenter-and-nsx/optimized-update-of-vcenter-and-nsx-manager.html' target='_blank'>View Documentation</a>)."
